{"sn35.113:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.113 ","sn35.113:0.2":"11. Yogakkhemivagga ","sn35.113:0.3":"Upassutisutta ","sn35.113:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava natike viharati ginjakavasathe. ","sn35.113:1.2":"Atha kho bhagava rahogato patisallino imam dhammapariyayam abhasi: ","sn35.113:1.3":"“cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.113:1.4":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.113:1.5":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn35.113:1.6":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn35.113:1.7":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn35.113:1.8":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn35.113:1.9":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn35.113:1.10":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn35.113:1.11":"Jivhanca paticca rase ca uppajjati …pe… ","sn35.113:1.12":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.113:1.13":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.113:1.14":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn35.113:1.15":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn35.113:1.16":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn35.113:1.17":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn35.113:1.18":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn35.113:1.19":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn35.113:2.1":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.113:2.2":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.113:2.3":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn35.113:2.4":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn35.113:2.5":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho; ","sn35.113:2.6":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho; ","sn35.113:2.7":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","sn35.113:2.8":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti …pe… ","sn35.113:2.9":"jivhanca paticca rase ca uppajjati …pe… ","sn35.113:2.10":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn35.113:2.11":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn35.113:2.12":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn35.113:2.13":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn35.113:2.14":"upadananirodha …pe… ","sn35.113:2.15":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti”ti. ","sn35.113:3.1":"Tena kho pana samayena annataro bhikkhu bhagavato upassuti thito hoti. ","sn35.113:3.2":"Addasa kho bhagava tam bhikkhum upassuti thitam. ","sn35.113:3.3":"Disvana tam bhikkhum etadavoca: ","sn35.113:3.4":"“assosi no tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayan”ti? ","sn35.113:3.5":"“Evam, bhante”. ","sn35.113:3.6":"“Ugganhahi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam. ","sn35.113:3.7":"Pariyapunahi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam. ","sn35.113:3.8":"Dharehi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam. ","sn35.113:3.9":"Atthasanhitoyam, bhikkhu, dhammapariyayo adibrahmacariyako”ti. ","sn35.113:3.10":"Dasamam. ","sn35.113:3.11":"Yogakkhemivaggo pathamo. ","sn35.113:4.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn35.113:4.1":"Yogakkhemi upadaya, ","sn35.113:4.2":"Dukkham loko ca seyyo ca; ","sn35.113:4.3":"Samyojanam upadanam, ","sn35.113:4.4":"Dve parijanam upassutiti. "}